rows.label: tlk001901_05_msg0001
rows.name: You're back from Acedia, aren't you?

rows.label: tlk001901_05_msg0002
rows.name:
What was it like there? I hope they
treat children well, if nothing else!

rows.label: tlk001901_05_msg0003
rows.name:
The boys're dead set on going to the
Academy, but we don't know what to
expect, so it worries me a little...

rows.label: tlk001901_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I just hope they manage to fit in with
the other kids, really.
